<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3826627>
    dc:description "Figs. 1–6. Habitus. 1. Ectaetia betzi sp.nov., male holotype. 2. Psectrosciara gonzalezae sp.nov., female paratype. 3. Scatopse notata (Linnaeus), female. 4. Aztecatopse huertai sp.nov., female paratype. 5. Swammerdamella marginata Cook, male. 6. Swammerdamella marginata Cook, female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3826627/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3826635>
    dc:description "Figs. 15–20. Abdomen. 15. Ectaetia betzi sp.nov, male holotype. 16. Psectrosciara gonzalezae sp.nov., female paratype. 17. Scatopse notata (Linnaeus), female. 18. Aztecatopse huertai sp.nov., female paratype. 19. Coboldia fuscipes (Meigen), male. 20. Coboldia fuscipes (Meigen), female (white arrow indicates the diagnostic lunulate sternite 7 posterior incision)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3826635/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3826655>
    dc:description "Figs. 47–51. Holoplagia guamensis (Johannsen), male. 47. Head, lateral view. 48.Thorax, lateral view. 49.Wing. 50. Segment 8 and terminalia, ventral view. 51. Segment 8 and terminalia, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3826655/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3826637>
    dc:description "Figs. 21–23. Abdomen. 21. Swammerdamella marginata Cook, male. 22. Swammerdamella marginata Cook, female. 23. Quateiella quatei (Cook), male. 24. Quateiella quatei (Cook), female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3826637/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3826629>
    dc:description "Figs. 7–10. Habitus. 7. Coboldia fuscipes (Meigen), male (black arrow indicates the diagnostic tergite 8 spatulate projection). 8. Coboldia fuscipes (Meigen), female. 9. Quateiella quatei (Cook), male. 10. Quateiella quatei (Cook), female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3826629/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3826633>
    dc:description "Figs. 11–14. Habitus. 11. Abrhexosa grossa (Cook), male. 12. Akorhexosa grossa (Cook), female. 13. 10. Abrhexosa ryckmani (Cook), male. 14. Cooka melanderi (Cook), male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3826633/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3826639>
    dc:description "Figs. 25–27. Abdomen.25. Akorhexosa grossa (Cook), male. 26. Akorhexosa grossa (Cook), female. 27. Cooka melanderi (Cook), male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3826639/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

